Package: rollply
Title: Moving-window add-on for plyr
Version: 0.4
Authors@R: "Alexandre Genin <alex@lecairn.org> [aut, cre]"
Description: Applies a a function in a moving window, over a dataset, then 
             combine the results.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.1)
Imports: 
    plyr,
    Rcpp,
    scales,
    alphahull,
    stringr
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: testthat,
          knitr, 
          proj4, 
          ggplot2,
          rgdal,
          tidyr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
